####################################################

DESCRIPTION : THIS IS TO DO THE SHM UPGRADE ACTIVITY FOR BSC NODES

USAGE : sh trigger.sh <num_of_nodes>

####################################################

This script will execute the mml and netconf commands by connecting to the node.

Pre Use-case Set up-
    1) The node details that is node name and node ip should be kept in a file called nodeips.txt like <nodename> <nodeip>

USECASE-
    The usecase should be triggered from the client server.
    sh trigger.sh <num_of_nodes>
    nodeips.txt file should be present in the client server.

####################################################
